```

### 2. Base Commit Determination
```yaml
# Default: Latest main branch
No commit specified â†’ git checkout -b hotfix/NAME origin/main

# Specific commit: Use provided hash
abc1234 provided â†’ git checkout -b hotfix/NAME abc1234

# Specific base branch
--base production â†’ git checkout -b hotfix/NAME origin/production
```

